      • huntForTheScriptFile

        public static java.io.File huntForTheScriptFile(java.lang.String input,
                                                java.lang.String[] standardExtensions)
                                         throws java.io.IOException
        Hunt for the script file, doesn't bother if it is named precisely. Tries in this order: - actual supplied name - name.ex - name.exertlet - name.sorcer.netlet - name.net - name.groovy - name.gvy - name.gy - name.gsh
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
